This File should contain on the Top 3 Lines
Author Name
Mod Name
Mod Branch on Github

Using this Repo as an Example
https://github.com/MrFlufficans/DK2ModderUtilities
                      Author       Mod Name
Mod Branch can be found on the Repository quite literally the Branch, Yours most likely is named Main

The Alternative is to Put the Download Link on Line One
Which will look like this

https://github.com/MrFlufficans/DK2ModderUtilities/archive/refs/heads/master.zip
                     Author          Mod Name                         Branch

